      "testimonials_bANPep": {
        "type": "testimonials",
        "blocks": {
          "testimonial_FmHxe6": {
            "type": "testimonial",
            "settings": {
              "rating": 5,
              "content": "<p>Such a cute product! Got the sleeping cat lamp for my daughter. She absolutely loves it. The quality is superb and delivery was on time!!</p>",
              "name": "Neha Kapoor",
              "bio": "Delhi"
            }
          },
          "testimonial_mbKAU3": {
            "type": "testimonial",
            "settings": {
              "rating": 5,
              "content": "<p><em>I honestly wasn’t sure what to expect, since it was my first time ordering from Bangshop. But the entire experience was smooth—from browsing the site to placing the order and getting it delivered on time. The packaging felt premium and the product looked exactly like the images. I’ve already recommended it to two of my friends.</em></p>",
              "name": "Ayesha Khan",
              "bio": "Delhi"
            }
          },
          "testimonial_brYDHN": {
            "type": "testimonial",
            "settings": {
              "rating": 5,
              "content": "<p>What I loved most was how easy the site was to use. Everything was well-categorized, the filters actually worked, and the checkout process was lightning fast. Plus, my order came earlier than expected, and I got constant updates on its status. Definitely one of the better online shopping experiences I’ve had.</p>",
              "name": "nitin sharma",
              "bio": "Mumbai"
            }
          },
          "testimonial_xhCK3A": {
            "type": "testimonial",
            "settings": {
              "rating": 5,
              "content": "<p>I ordered a self-care gift box for my sister’s birthday and the moment it arrived, I was blown away. The packaging was so elegant and thoughtful that it looked way more expensive than what I actually paid. My sister absolutely loved it. Will definitely order again when I need a gift that makes an impression.</p>",
              "name": "Rohan Mehta",
              "bio": "Mumbai"
